Text: Hesters New Email Address Cc All Well we finally got tired of dealing with Prodigy they bought out FlashNet our old ISP and slow internet connections and broke down and got RoadRunner The new mailbox is The old address will still be active until May th but after that date I dont think we will be able to retrieve mail to that address
